Fans and musicians gathered in the Sandton Convention Centre to commemorate the life of musician Johnny Clegg on July 26 2019. Clegg passed away on July 17 2019 after a long battle with pancreatic cancer. The memorial service had a brief program that was lead by actor John Kani as director, withÂ performances by Soweto Gospel Choir, Zolani Mahola and Sipho Mchunu.